36061651%2Famp%2F%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2024%2Ffilm%2Freviews%2Fthree-days-of-fish-review-1236061651%2Famp%2F%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Woman%20Falls%20Ill%2C%20Throws%20Up%20On%20Flight%2C%20Doctor%20Uses%20Smartwatch%20To%20Diagnose%20Her%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EOn%20an%20Air%20India%20flight%20going%20from%20Delhi%20to%20San%20Francisco%2C%20a%20passenger%20experiencing%20a%20medical%20emergency%20was%20promptly%20saved%20by%20a%20doctor%20with%20the%20help%20of%20an%20Apple%20watch.%20The%20incident%20happened%20on%20July%202%20after%20a%2056-year-old%20woman%20fell%20ill%20mid-flight%2C%20feeling%20dizzy%20and%20throwing%20up%20repeatedly.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Gigy%20V.%20Kuruttukulam%2C%20medical%20director%20at%20Kerala's%20Rajagiri%20Hospital%2C%20who%20was%20the%20only%20doctor%20on%20board%2C%20came%20to%20the%20woman's%20rescue.%20After%20presenting%20his%20ID%20card%20to%20the%20flight%20officials%2C%20he%20proceeded%20to%20examine%20the%20woman.%20With%20no%20medical%20equipment%20on%20him%2C%20he%20asked%20her%20to%20lie%20down%20and%20used%20the%20Apple%20smart%20watch%20she%20was%20wearing%20to%20monitor%20her%20heartbeat%20and%20oxygen%20saturation.%20He%20also%20conducted%20an%20electrocardiogram%20test%20with%20the%20help%20of%20the%20watch.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20found%20out%20that%20the%20woman's%20oxygen%20saturation%20was%20low%20and%20her%20blood%20pressure%20was%20elevated%20and%20administered%20her%20necessary%20injections%20available%20in%20the%20flight's%20medical%20kit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Gigy's%20swift%20response%20also%20averted%20flight%20delay.%20As%20the%20captain%20considered%20diverting%20the%20flight%20to%20the%20nearest%20airport%2C%20Dr%20Gigy%20assured%20him%20that%20the%20woman%20was%20stable%20and%20will%20be%20able%20to%20make%20the%20journey%2C%20reducing%20the%20arrival%20time%20to%20San%20Francisco%20by%2015%20minutes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUpon%20arriving%20at%20the%20San%20Francisco%20airport%2C%20a%20medical%20team%20was%20ready%20to%20take%20the%20woman%20to%20a%20hospital.%20She%20was%20admitted%20to%20an%20ICU%20where%20she%20is%20recovering%2C%20said%20the%20hospital%20staff.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20flights%2C%20doctors%20are%20not%20allowed%20to%20administer%20any%20medication%20or%20treatment%20without%20verification%20of%20their%20identity.%20Dr%20Gigy%20highlighted%20the%20importance%20of%20doctors%20carrying%20their%20ID%20cards%20on%20flights.%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1720269240000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2Furspbplg_air-india-flight-emergency_625x300_06_July_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwoman-falls-ill-throws-up-on-flight-doctor-uses-smartwatch-to-diagnose-her-6047603%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22On%20an%20Air%20India%20flight%20going%20from%20Delhi%20to%20San%20Francisco%2C%20a%20passenger%20experiencing%20a%20medical%20emergency%20was%20promptly%20saved%20by%20a%20doctor%20with%20the%20help%20of%20an%20Apple%20watch.%20The%20incident%20happened%20on%20July%202.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwoman-falls-ill-throws-up-on-flight-doctor-uses-smartwatch-to-diagnose-her-6047603%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwoman-falls-ill-throws-up-on-flight-doctor-uses-smartwatch-to-diagnose-her-6047603%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwoman-falls-ill-throws-up-on-flight-doctor-uses-smartwatch-to-diagnose-her-6047603%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22I%20want%20to%20retire%20before%2050%2C%20so%20I%20asked%20a%20financial%20planner%20for%203%20ways%20to%20earn%20more%20on%20my%20savings%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20offers%20and%20details%20on%20this%20page%20may%20have%20updated%20or%20chan