20a%20few%20years%20after%20Biden's%20election%2C%20Kaufman%20became%20his%20chief%20of%20staff.%20When%20Biden%20left%20the%20Senate%20after%20being%20elected%20vice%20president%20in%202009%2C%20Kaufman%20replaced%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe's%20been%20described%20as%20Biden's%20best%20friend%20and%20his%20alter%20ego.%20Kaufman%20has%20also%20told%20Biden%20the%20harsh%20truth%20before.%20In%201987%2C%20it%20was%20Kaufman%20who%20urged%20the%20then-senator%20to%20drop%20out%20of%20the%20presidential%20race%20amid%20a%20plagiarism%20scandal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B%3Cspan%3EThere's%20only%20one%20way%20to%20stop%20the%20sharks%20and%20that's%20pull%20out%2C%26quot%3B%20Kaufman%20told%20Biden%2C%20according%20to%20The%20New%20York%20Times.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBiden%20often%20returns%20to%20Delaware%20on%20the%20weekends.%20According%20to%20The%20Times%2C%20when%20the%20president%20goes%20home%20he%20seeks%20out%20Kaufman.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERon%20Klain%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ron%20Klain%20shakes%20Joe%20Biden's%20hand%20during%20a%20White%20House%20event%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66887a03268f62ba18a7e4f8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22696%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EFormer%20White%20House%20chief%20of%20staff%20Ron%20Klain%20is%20so%20close%20to%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20that%20he%20has%20been%20viewed%20as%20a%20quasi-son.%3Cp%3EKevin%20Dietsch%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EFormer%20White%20House%20chief%20of%20staff%20Ron%20Klain%20is%20at%20the%20center%20of%20Biden's%20debate%20debacle.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKlain%20has%20prepped%20Democrats%20for%20presidential%20debates%20for%20decades.%20He%20took%20time%20away%20from%20his%20new%20job%20with%20AirBnb%20to%20help%20prepare%20his%20old%20boss.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Indiana%20native%20has%20worked%20for%20Biden%20almost%20nonstop%20since%20graduating%20from%20Harvard%20Law%20School%20in%201987.%20Under%20Biden's%20leadership%2C%20he%20was%20chief%20counsel%20to%20the%20Senate%20Judiciary%20Committee.%20After%20serving%20as%20Vice%20President%20Al%20Gore's%20chief%20of%20staff%2C%20Klain%20returned%20to%20the%20role%20during%20the%20Obama%20administration.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKlain's%20decision%20to%20back%20former%20Secretary%20of%20State%20Hillary%20Clinton%20ahead%20of%20the%202016%20Democratic%20primary%20over%20Biden%2C%20who%20was%20still%20musing%20about%20his%20run%2C%20was%20considered%20a%20deep%20act%20of%20betrayal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Klain%20returned%20to%20the%20Biden%20orbit%20and%20realized%20his%20long-held%20ambition%20of%20being%20the%20top%20aide%20to%20a%20president.%20It's%20their%20closeness%20that%20might%20make%20it%20hard%20for%20Biden's%20former%20chief%20to%20pressure%20his%20long-time%20boss%20to%20step%20aside.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B%3Cspan%3EHe's%20like%20a%20father%20to%20Ron%20Klain.%20What%20do%20you%20say%20to%20your%20father%3F%20This%20is%20tough%2C%20very%20tough%2C%26quot%3B%20Elaine%20Kamarck%2C%20a%20longtime%20member%20of%20the%20Democratic%20National%20Committee%2C%20told%20The%20Times.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20The%20Times%2C%20Biden%20still%20talks%20to%20him%20once%20a%20week%20to%20figure%20out%20the%20best%20ways%20to%20attack%20Trump.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EMike%20Donilon%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Mike%20Donilon%2C%20Joe%20Biden%2C%20and%20Bruce%20Reed%20walk%20along%20the%20White%20House%20grounds%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66887f33268f62ba18a7e54a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221667%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMike%20Donilon%2C%20a%20longtime%20aide%20to%20President%20Joe%20Biden%2C%20left%20the%20White%20House%20to%20help%20with%20Biden's%20reelection.%3Cp%3EChip%20Somodevilla%2FGetty%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ELike%2