l%20emphasized%20that%20financial%20transactions%2C%20money%20trails%2C%20and%20call%20records%20associated%20with%20Madhukar%20are%20currently%20under%20scrutiny.%20The%20police%20are%20also%20planning%20to%20seek%20his%20remand%20for%20further%20questioning.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20initial%20probe%20into%20the%20stampede%20had%20revealed%20that%20the%20godman%20had%20received%20permission%20to%20host%20an%20event%20for%2080%2C000%20people%2C%20but%202.5%20lakh%20people%20were%20allowed%20to%20enter%20the%20venue.%20After%20the%20gathering%2C%20when%20the%20'godman'%20was%20leaving%2C%20there%20was%20a%20rush%20among%20his%20followers%20to%20collect%20dust%20stirred%20up%20by%20his%20car's%20tyres.%20According%20to%20officials%2C%20the%20godman's%20private%20security%20guards%20started%20pushing%20his%20followers%20and%20some%20people%20fell%20and%20were%20trampled.%20In%20the%20chaos%2C%20many%20others%20fled%20towards%20the%20open%20field%20and%20slipped%2C%20and%20others%20ran%20over%20them.%20Many%20of%20those%20killed%20in%20the%20stampede%20were%20women%20and%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20eyewitnesses%2C%20only%20about%2040%20police%20personnel%20were%20on%20duty%20to%20ensure%20safety%20at%20this%20massive%20gathering%20and%20they%20were%20overwhelmed%20when%20the%20stampede%20broke%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMadhukar%20was%20the%20'mukhya%20sevadar'%20(chief%20of%20security)%20of%20the%20'satsang'%20where%20the%20stampede%20occurred.%20He%20is%20the%20only%20accused%20named%20in%20the%20FIR%20lodged%20at%20Sikandra%20Rao%20police%20station%20in%20Hathras%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20incident%2C%20and%20Suraj%20Pal%20Singh%20hasn't%20been%20named.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInitially%2C%20Madhukar's%20lawyer%2C%20AP%20Singh%2C%20had%20asserted%20that%20his%20client%20had%20voluntarily%20surrendered%20to%20the%20Delhi%20police%20for%20medical%20treatment.%20However%2C%20Hathras%20police%20said%20they%20arrested%20Madhukar%20through%20technical%20surveillance%2C%20offering%20a%20reward%20of%20one%20lakh%20rupees%20for%20information%20leading%20to%20his%20arrest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Saturday%20afternoon%2C%20amidst%20tight%20security%20arrangements%2C%20Madhukar%20was%20brought%20to%20the%20Bagla%20Combined%20District%20Hospital%20in%20Hathras%20for%20a%20medical%20examination.%20He%20appeared%20with%20his%20face%20covered%20by%20a%20handkerchief%20and%20a%20stole%20wrapped%20around%20his%20head.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20three-member%20judicial%20commission%20team%20has%20arrived%20in%20Hathras%20to%20investigate%20administrative%20lapses%20that%20may%20have%20contributed%20to%20the%20tragedy.%20Statements%20from%20multiple%20officials%20have%20been%20recorded%2C%20and%20the%20team%20visited%20the%20site%20of%20the%20incident%20to%20gather%20further%20evidence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAuthorities%20plan%20to%20delve%20deeper%20into%20Madhukar's%20association%20with%20Bhole%20Baba's%20trust%2C%20scrutinizing%20funding%20sources%20and%20bank%20accounts.%20They%20intend%20to%20collaborate%20with%20other%20agencies%20to%20probe%20potential%20political%20links%20to%20the%20case.%20Should%20it%20be%20deemed%20necessary%2C%20a%20summons%20may%20also%20be%20issued%20to%20Bhole%20Baba%20for%20questioning.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20conducting%20a%20thorough%20investigation%20into%20Madhukar's%20background%20and%20his%20role%20in%20the%20incident%2C%26quot%3B%20stated%20SP%20Nipun%20Agarwal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20any%20political%20is%20found%20to%20be%20associated%20with%20(Bhole%20Baba's)%20organisation%2C%20we%20will%20take%20action%20against%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20if%20the%20self-styled%20godman%20may%20be%20arrested%2C%20state%20police%20chief%20Prashant%20Kumar%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BRight%20now%2C%20everything%20is%20a%20matter%20of%20investigation.%20We%20do%20not%20want%20to%20influence%20the%20investigation%20by%20drawing%20any%20immediate%20