%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%2080%2F20%20rule%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20means%20she%20eats%20a%20healthy%20diet%20of%20mainly%20whole%20foods%2080%25%20of%20the%20time%20and%20whatever%20she%20wants%20for%20the%20other%2020%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20might%20be%20added%20sugar%2C%20that%20might%20be%20ultra-processed%20food.%20But%20I%20do%20it%20completely%20guilt-free%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20This%20helps%20her%20cut%20down%20on%20UPFs%20without%20limiting%20herself%20too%20much.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20healthy%20diet%20in%20the%20long%20term%20is%20all%20about%20a%20dietary%20pattern%20that%20looks%20at%20the%20diet%20as%20a%20whole%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20that%20in%20mind%2C%20Patel%20has%20three%20go-to%20breakfasts%20she%20alternates%20between%20so%20she%20doesn't%20get%20bored.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222a17d272-124c-4a8c-9745-f9c596ee9eec%5C%22%3EOvernight%20oats%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EPatel%20is%20a%20big%20fan%20of%20oats%20because%20they%20contain%20lots%20of%20fiber%20and%20are%20slow-release%20carbohydrates%2C%20which%20gives%20her%20sustained%20energy%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20likes%20to%20make%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhealthy-oat-based-breakfast-recipes-for-fat-loss-muscle-gain-2021-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eovernight%20oats%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20load%20them%20with%20nutrients%20and%20protein.%20She%20mixes%20the%20oats%20with%20soy%20milk%20and%20adds%20Greek%20yogurt%20for%20protein%20and%20for%20her%20gut%20health%2C%20as%20it's%20a%20fermented%20food%20that%20contains%20probiotics.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20top%2C%20she%20sprinkles%20lots%20of%20chia%20seeds%20to%20boost%20the%20fiber%20content%20of%20her%20oats%2C%20and%20berries%20for%20micronutrients.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20that%20swapping%20sugar-sweetened%20yogurt%2C%20which%20is%20typically%20ultra-processed%2C%20for%20Greek%20yogurt%20with%20fruit%20can%20be%20a%20good%20place%20to%20start%20reducing%20your%20intake%20of%20UPFs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BStart%20thinking%20about%20how%20you%20could%20make%20a%20simple%20swap%20to%20maybe%20something%20that%20is%20less%20processed%2C%26quot%3B%20Patel%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Overnight%20oats.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F63763518102fec00126e0ec7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223337%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EOvernight%20oats%20are%20a%20great%20make-ahead%20breakfast%20that%20can%20be%20eaten%20on%20the%20go.%3Cp%3EGetty%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22db2b5896-7014-4fde-8dfc-acb16a6e888c%5C%22%3EEggs%20and%20avocado%20on%20toast%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EPatel%20has%20recently%20gotten%20into%20baking%20bread%2C%20and%20because%20toast%20is%20quick%20and%20easy%2C%20she%20regularly%20has%20it%20for%20breakfast.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20she's%20buying%20bread%2C%20she'll%20go%20for%20sourdough%20as%20it's%20fermented%2C%20or%20something%20wholewheat%20with%20seeds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSometimes%20I%20boil%20eggs%20while%20I%20shower%2C%20mash%20avocado%20with%20it%2C%20and%20then%20put%20it%20on%20toast%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEggs%20are%20a%20great%20source%20of%20protein%20and%20vitamins%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Feating-avocado-a-week-reduces-risk-of-heart-disease-study-2022-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eavocados%3C%2Fa%3E%20contain%20healthy%20fats%2C%20fiber%2C%20and%20antioxidants.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%223f7b7fa5-7111-48f4-b8b7-4585c6f6fc7a%5C%22%3ENut%20butter%20and%20fruit%20on%20toast%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20she's%20craving%20something%20sweet%2C%20Patel%20has%20toast%20with%20nut%20butter%20and%20fresh%20fruit.%20She%20chooses%20a%20loaf%20of%20bread%20and%20nut%20butter%20with%20the%20shortest%20ingredients%20list.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENuts%20are%20a%20good%20source%20of%20protein%20and%20nut%20butter%20is%20considered%20processed%2C%20not%20ultra-processed%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20instead%20of%20jelly%2C%20which%20is%20high%20in%20sugar%2C%20she%20tops%20her%20toast%20with%20sliced%20fruit%20or%20mashes%20some%20raspberries%20on%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdietitian-researches-ultra-processed-foods-shares-easy-breakfasts-2024-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1720262582000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6683d7d4268f62ba18a680d6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdietitian-researches-ultra-processed-foods-shares-easy-breakfasts-2024-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20dietitian%20follows%20the%2080%2F20%20rule%20to%20help%20her%20avoid%20ultra-processed%20foods.%20Her%20favorite%20easy%2C%20healthy%20breakfasts%20include%20overnight%20oats.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22kschewitz%40businessinsider.com%20(Kim%20Schewitz)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A8%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdietitian-researches-ultra-processed-foods-shares-easy-breakfasts-2024-7%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22My%203%20high-yield%20savings%20accounts%20have%20helped%20me%20meet%20goals%20that%20seemed%20impossible%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20offers%20and%20details%20on%20this%20page%20may%20have%20updated%20or%20changed%20since%20the%20time%20of%20publication.%20See%20our%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fuse-several-high-yield-savings-accounts-reach-goals-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20current%20information.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAffiliate%20links%20for%20the%20products%20on%20this%20page%20are%20from%20partners%20that%20compensate%20us%20and%20terms%20apply%20to%20offers%20listed%20(see%20o