w.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fbest-high-yield-savings-accounts-rates-right-now%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebest%20high-yield%20savings%20account%20rates%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Because%20interest%20rates%20are%20always%20fluctuating%20(I've%20received%2015%20emails%20over%20the%20past%20year%20telling%20me%20that%20Ally%20increased%20my%20rate%2C%20again)%2C%20and%20the%20features%20of%20many%20accounts%20are%20the%20same%2C%20there%20really%20is%20no%20%26quot%3Bbest%26quot%3B%20account.%20As%20long%20as%20the%20account%20doesn't%20have%20any%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fmonthly-bank-maintenance-fee%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebank%20maintenance%20fees%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20using%20any%20HYSA%20is%20far%20better%20than%20using%20a%20%26quot%3Btraditional%26quot%3B%20savings%20account.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%221a44d709-53d7-4b55-a972-f773a63e5d97%5C%22%3EMy%20first%20high-yield%20savings%20account%20was%20with%20Ally%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20started%20my%20savings%20journey%2C%20I%20opened%20my%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fally-high-yield-savings-account-review%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAlly%20high-yield%20savings%20account%3C%2Fa%3E%20after%20reading%20articles%20that%20compared%20different%20banks%20and%20seeing%20that%20name%20come%20up%20often.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOverall%2C%20I've%20been%20satisfied%20with%20this%20choice%2C%20and%20it's%20worked%20well%20for%20me.%20I%20started%20saving%20my%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fwhat-is-an-emergency-fund%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eemergency%20fund%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20this%20account.%20Experts%20recommend%20you%20begin%20with%20an%20emergency%20fund%2C%20because%20it%20becomes%20incredibly%20challenging%20to%20save%20for%20anything%20else%20if%20you%20need%20to%20withdraw%20funds%20anytime%20something%20unexpected%20happens.%20My%20emergency%20fund%20allows%20me%20to%20create%20a%20stable%20foundation%20for%20my%20savings%20journey.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20thing%20I%20like%20about%20Ally%20is%20its%20%26quot%3Bsavings%20buckets%26quot%3B%20feature%2C%20which%20allows%20you%20to%20set%20up%20multiple%20sinking%20funds%20%E2%80%94%20or%20savings%20accounts%20for%20different%20goals%20%E2%80%94%20in%20one%20place.%20Many%20users%20take%20advantage%20of%20this%20benefit%20and%20use%20this%20approach%20to%20save%20up%20for%20their%20various%20goals.%20Some%20common%20%26quot%3Bbuckets%26quot%3B%20are%20emergency%20funds%2C%20holiday%20savings%2C%20and%20vacation%20funds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20this%20is%20a%20useful%20strategy%20if%20it%20works%20for%20you%2C%20I%20knew%20that%20it%20wasn't%20the%20one%20that%20would%20allow%20me%20to%20save%20the%20most.%20I%20decided%20to%20open%20another%20HYSA%20instead%2C%20because%20I%20prefer%20keeping%20my%20sinking%20funds%20at%20different%20banks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22eca081a1-c91d-430a-996c-8fe0038a14bf%5C%22%3EI%20have%202%20more%20accounts%20with%20Capital%20One%20360%20for%20long-term%20goals%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20chose%20to%20open%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fcapital-one-360-savings-account-interest-rate-how-it-compares%5C%22%3ECapital%20One%20360%20savings%20account%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20because%20they%20had%20a%20generous%20new%20user%20bonus%20when%20I%20signed%20up.%20Capital%20One's%20interest%20rate%20was%20comparable%20to%20Ally's%20when%20I%20signed%20up%2C%20and%20I%20haven't%20seen%20a%20significant%20difference%20in%20interest%20deposits.%20I%20opened%20this%20account%20to%20save%20for%20a%20major%20medical%20expense%20%E2%80%94%20InvisAlign%20%E2%80%94%20and%20I%20was%20able%20to%20reach%20my%20goal%20quickly%20due%20to%20the%20high%20interest%20rate%2C%20the%20bonus%2C%20and%20my%20sole%20focus%20on%20that%20goal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECurrently%2C%20I%20have%20one%20account%20with%20Ally%20and%20two%20with%20Capital%20One.%20I've%20kept%20my%20emergency%20fund%20in%20Ally%20throughout%20this%20time%2C%20and%20the%20total%20has%20rarely%20dipped%20below%20%246%2C000%20(roughly%20six%20months%20of%20bare-bone%20necessities%20for%20me).%20I%20receive%20my%20monthly%20interest%20deposit%20every%20month%2C%20which%20is%20a%20nice%20little%20bonus%20that%20helps%20keep%20the%20fund%20padded.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20Capital%20One%20accounts%20are%20more%20active.%20I%20use%20the%20savings%20account%20for%20longer-term%20savings%20(right%20now%2C%20an%20upcoming%20extended%20time%20off%20from%20work)%20and%20the%20checking%20account%20for%20shorter-term%20goals%2C%20like%20buying%20a%20new%20iPad.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFeatured%20Nationally%20Available%20Deposit%20Rates%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ctable%20border%3D%5C%221%5C%22%3E%3Ctbody%3E%3Ctr%3E%3Ctd%3EAccount%20Name%3C%2Ftd%3E%3Ctd%3EAPY%20(Annual%20Percentage%20Yield)%20Accurate%20as%20of%207%2F3%2F2024%3C%2Ftd%3E%3Ctd%3EMinimum%20Account%20Opening%20Balance%3C%2Ftd%3E%3C%2Ftr%3E%3Ctr%3E%3Ctd%3EWestern%20Alliance%20Bank%20High-Yield%20Savings%20Premier%3C%2Ftd%3E%3Ctd%3E5.36%25%3C%2Ftd%3E%3Ctd%3E%24500%3C%2Ftd%3E%3C%2Ftr%3E%3Ctr%3E%3Ctd%3EBrioDirect%20High-Yield%20Savings%20Account%3C%2Ftd%3E%3Ctd%3E5.30%25%3C%2Ftd%3E%3Ctd%3E%245%2C000%3C%2Ftd%3E%3C%2Ftr%3E%3Ctr%3E%3Ctd%3EForbright%20Growth%20Savings%3C%2Ftd%3E%3Ctd%3E5.30%25%3C%2Ftd%3E%3Ctd%3E%240%3C%2Ftd%3E%3C%2Ftr%3E%3Ctr%3E%3Ctd%3ECIT%20Bank%20Platinum%20Savings%3C%2Ftd%3E%3Ctd%3E5.00%25%20(with%20%245%2C000%20minimum%20balance)%3C%2Ftd%3E%3Ctd%3E%24100%3C%2Ftd%3E%3C%2Ftr%3E%3Ctr%3E%3Ctd%3EBarclays%20Online%20Savings%20Account%3C%2Ftd%3E%3Ctd%3E4.35%25%3C%2Ftd%3E%3Ctd%3E%240%3C%2Ftd%3E%3C%2Ftr%3E%3Ctr%3E%3Ctd%3ECapital%20One%20360%20Performance%20Savings%3C%2Ftd%3E%3Ctd%3E4.25%25%3C%2Ftd%3E%3Ctd%3E%240%3C%2Ftd%3E%3C%2Ftr%3E%3C%2Ftbody%3E%3C%2Ftable%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a921fb20-8276-41df-9478-61b4f2b71176%5C%22%3EI%20allocate%20different%20amounts%20to%20each%20of%20my%20accounts%20each%20month%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EUsing%20these%20accounts%20in%20this%20manner%20has%20allowed%20me%20to%20reach%20a%20number%20of%20goals%20over%20the%20past%20three%20years%20that%20may%20have%20seemed%20impossible%20on%20a%20teacher's%20salary%20(a%20%245%2C000%20car%2C%20%246%2C000%20InvisAlign%2C%20my%20%245%2C000-plus%20trip%20to%20the%20Maldives%2C%20and%20now%20a%20long-term%20break%20from%20work).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20my%20emergency%20fund%20was%20where%20I%20needed%20it%20to%20be%2C%20I%20consistently%20allocated%20%24100%20to%20%24200%20a%20month%20to%20the%20other%20accounts%20and%20made%20those%20the%20priority.%20This%20often%20meant%20declining%20other%20things%20I%20may%20have%20wanted%20%E2%80%94%20I%20buy%20very%20few%20material%20items%20%E2%80%94%20and%20instead%20prioritizing%20what%20was%20most%20important%20to%20me.%20Using%20high-yield%20savings%20accounts%20with%20high%20interest%20rates%20helped%2C%20allowing%20me%20to%20get%20a%20small%20bonus%20deposit%20each%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20excitement%20about%20HYSAs%20continues%20to%20bloom%2C%20I%20recommend%20not%20spending%20too%20much%20time%20stressing%20about%20which%20account%20is%20the%20%26quot%3Bbest%26quot%3B%20and%20just%20getting%20started.%20I%20read%20more%20articles%20than%20I%20needed%20to%20and%20ended%20up%20opening%20different%20accounts%20anyway.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20interest%20rates%20varying%20between%204%25%20and%205.50%25%20and%20always%20changing%2C%20I'm%20happy%20with%20most%20HYSAs%20without%20fees.%20Small%2C%20consistent%20deposits%20and%20sinking%20funds%20placed%20in%20different%20accounts%20have%20allowed%20my%20savings%20to%20add%20up%20faster%20than%20I%20might%20have%20thought%20was%20possible.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20was%20originally%20published%20in%20August%202023.%3C%2Fem%3E%