calUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpolitical-slugfest-over-sword-attack-on-punjab-shiv-sena-leader-6046308%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpolitical-slugfest-over-sword-attack-on-punjab-shiv-sena-leader-6046308%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpolitical-slugfest-over-sword-attack-on-punjab-shiv-sena-leader-6046308%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20Message%20to%20Opposition%3A%20If%20You%20Want%20To%20Be%20Heard%2C%20Listen%20Too%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2F4dlbpp5_rahul-gandhi-ani_625x300_25_June_24.jpg%3Fim%3DFitAndFill%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMark%20Twain%20once%20said%20that%20%26quot%3Bfacts%20are%20stubborn%2C%20but%20statistics%20are%20more%20pliable.%26quot%3B%20At%20the%20end%20of%20the%20seven-day%20first%20session%20of%20the%2018th%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20Speaker%20Om%20Birla%20stated%20that%20the%20House%20had%20operated%20at%20103%25%20productivity.%20In%20recent%20years%2C%20disrupted%20sittings%20have%20overshadowed%20the%20quality%20of%20debate%20and%20discussion%2C%20making%20productivity%20rather%20than%20substantive%20discourse%20the%20norm%20for%20assessing%20Parliament.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20session%20witnessed%20an%20unprecedented%20filibuster%20by%20the%20Opposition.%20The%20Leader%20of%20the%20Opposition%20(LoP)%2C%20Rahul%20Gandhi%2C%20was%20assertive%20and%20occasionally%20flouted%20norms.%20The%20Prime%20Minister%20spoke%20amidst%20continuous%20uproar%20from%20Opposition%20MPs%2C%20who%20gathered%20in%20the%20Well%20of%20the%20House%20and%20chanted%20slogans.%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi's%20ability%20to%20remain%20composed%20and%20deliver%20his%20speech%20amidst%20the%20chaos%20was%20commendable.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EModi%20intervened%20twice%20while%20the%20LoP%20was%20addressing%20the%20House.%20Defence%20Minister%20Rajnath%20Singh%2C%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%2C%20and%20Agriculture%20Minister%20Shivraj%20Chouhan%20also%20intervened%20to%20counter%20the%20LoP's%20allegations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Expunging%20Of%20Remarks%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Speaker%20Om%20Birla%20appeared%20lenient%20during%20the%20session%2C%20he%20later%20expunged%20several%20parts%20of%20the%20LoP's%20speech.%20In%20this%20era%20of%20live%20telecasts%20and%20digital%20media%2C%20the%20effectiveness%20of%20such%20a%20move%20is%20limited%3B%20they%20merely%20ensure%20that%20the%20expunged%20portions%20do%20not%20become%20part%20of%20the%20official%20House%20record.%20Rahul%20Gandhi's%20response%20was%20explicit%3A%20%26quot%3BIn%20Modiji's%20world%2C%20truth%20can%20be%20expunged.%20But%20in%20reality%2C%20truth%20can't%20be%20expunged.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETypically%2C%20MPs%20rely%20on%20notes%20containing%20references%20and%20talking%20points%20when%20speaking%20in%20Parliament.%20Rahul%20Gandhi's%20principal%20ally%2C%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%2C%20who%20abstained%20when%20the%20LoP%20spoke%20on%20Monday%2C%20was%20seen%20looking%20at%20notes%20the%20following%20day%20when%20he%20criticised%20the%20government%2C%20just%20before%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20responded%20to%20the%20Motion%20of%20Thanks%20to%20the%20President.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERahul%20Gandhi%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20did%20not%20refer%20to%20notes.%20He%20displayed%20images%20of%20Lord%20Shiva%20and%20Guru%20Nanak%20to%20bolster%20his%20arguments%2C%20in%20clear%20disregard%20of%20rules%20prohibiting%20such%20displays.%20In%20social%20media%20clips%2C%20he%20again%20showcased%20an%20image%20of%20Shiva%20on%20Thursday.%20Apart%20from%20his%20signature%20T-shirt%2C%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20now%20uses%20props%20like%20the%20Shiva%20image%20to%20emphasise%20his%20'nonconformity'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReferring%20to%20Rahul%20Gandhi's%20past%20allegations%20that%20did%20not%20stand%20up%20to%20scrutiny%20and%20even%20drew%20criticism%20from%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20quoted%20Tulsidas%3A%20%26quot%3B%3Cem%3EJhoothahi%20lena%2C%20jhoothahi%20dena%2C%20jhoothahi%20bhojan%2C%20jhooth%20chabena%3C%2Fem%3E%26quot%3B%20(accepting%20falsehood%2C%20spreading%20falsehood%2C%20eating%20falsehood%2C%20chewing%20falsehood).%20Interestingly%2C%20while%20quoting%20Tulsidas%2C%20Modi%20gestured%20to%20Akhilesh%2C%20who%20appreciated%20and%20echoed%20the%20quote%20along%20with%20the%20Prime%20Minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EModi's%20Rajya%20Sabha%20Address%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20following%20day%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%2C%20Modi%20cited%20the%20late%20Samajwadi%20Party%20(SP)%20patriarch%20Mulayam%20Singh%2C%20who%20in%202013%20had%20accused%20Congress%20of%20using%20the%20CBI%20and%20the%20ED%20for%20political%20harassment.%20Modi%20pointed%20out%20that%20cases%20were%20filed%20against%20Akhilesh%20upon%20his%20entry%20into%20politics%20during%20the%20Congress%20regime.%20Modi%20also%20noted%20that%20Congress%20had%20won%20more%20seats%20through%20alliances%20than%20on%20its%20own%2C%20describing%20the%20party%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bparasite%26quot%3B.%20Despite%20the%20rivalry%20between%20the%20SP%20and%20the%20BJP%2C%20Mulayam%20Singh%20Yadav%20had%20been%20an%20admirer%20of%20Modi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%2C%20Modi%20stated%20that%20the%20cases%20against%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20originated%20from%20allegations%20made%20by%20the%20Congress%2C%20which%20is%20now%20an%20ally%20of%20AAP.%20Two%20days%20later%2C%20Congress%20spokesperson%20Jairam%20Ramesh%20told%20PTI%20that%20there%20%26quot%3Bdoesn't%20appear%20to%20be%20much%20scope%26quot%3B%20for%20an%20alliance%20with%20AAP%20in%20Haryana%20and%20Delhi%20for%20the%20assembly%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWithout%20naming%20anyone%2C%20Modi%20attributed%20the%20Opposition's%20stance%20to%20'%3Cem%3Ebalak%20buddhi%3C%2Fem%3E'%20(infantile%20thought).%20In%201920%2C%20Vladimir%20Illych%20Lenin%20had%20warned%20against%20the%20forces%20of%20opportunism%20with%20a%20propensity%20to%20create%20anarchy%20in%20his%20booklet%2C%20Left%20Wing%20Communism%2C%20an%20Infantile%20Disorder.%20The%20Opposition's%20filibuster%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20while%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20spoke%20was%20visibly%20encouraged%20by%20the%20LoP%2C%20who%2C%20apart%20from%20the%20Speaker%20and%20Leader%20of%20the%20House%20(PM)%2C%20is%20a%20key%20figure%20in%20Parliament.%20Amidst%20continuous%20slogans%2C%20there%20was%20also%20a%20lighter%20moment%20when%20Modi%20offered%20a%20glass%20of%20water%20to%20MPs%20standing%20directly%20in%20front%20of%20him%20in%20the%20Well.%20Hibi%20Eden%20accepted%20the%20glass%2C%20drank%20from%20it%2C%20placed%20it%20back%20on%20the%20table%20in%20front%20of%20the%20PM%2C%20and%20continued%20disrupting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bedlam%20caused%20by%20the%20Opposition%20was%20somewhat%20hidden%20by%20the%20official%20telecast%20of%20proceedings%20on%20Sansad%20TV.%20Videos%20filmed%20by%20BJP%20MPs%20inside%20the%20House%20were%20uploaded%20by%20the%20BJP's%20media%20cell%20on%20digital%20platforms%20the%20following%20day.%20If%20Sansad%20TV%20had%20captured%20the%20unbecoming%20conduct%20of%20the%20Opposition-MPs%20reluctant%20to%20enter%20the%20Well%2C%20being%20prodded%20or%20even%20physically%20dragged%20at%20the%20behest%20of%20the%20LoP-the%20state%20of%20our%20Parliament%20in%20the%2075th%20year%20of%20the%20Republic%20would%20have%20been%20starkly%20highlighted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Responsibility%20To%20Listen%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20PM's%20reply%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20initially%20did%20not%20face%20slogans%20or%20disruptions.%20However%2C%20when%20he%20questioned%20Congress's%20commitment%20to%20the%20Constitution%2C%20Congress%20President%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20sought%20to%20intervene.%20Vice%20President%20Jagdip%20Dhankar's%20refusal%20prompted%20slogans%20and%20a%20subsequent%20walkout.%20Unlike%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20MPs%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20did%20not%20rush%20into%20the%20Well.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20the%20PM%20mentioned%20that%20despite%20his%20return%20to%20power%2C%20the%20Opposition's%20'ecosystem'%20was%20attempting%20to%20convince%20the%20public%20that%20the%20government%20had%20been%20'defeated'.%20As%20a%20pre-poll%20alliance%2C%20the%20NDA%20secured%20a%20clear%20majority.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20responsibility%20to%20listen%20and%20enable%20the%20optimal%20functioning%20of%20Parliament%20is%20intrinsic%20to%20the%20Opposition's%20right%20to%20be%20heard%20and%20assertive.%20This%20principle%20was%20abandoned%20during%20the%20first%20session%20of%20the%2018th%20Lok%20Sabha.%20The%20people's%20mandate%20must%20not%20be%20trivialised%20thus.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Shubhabrata%20Bhattacharya%20is%20a%20retired%20editor%20and%20a%20public%20affairs%20commentator)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1720261080000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2F4dlbpp5_rahul-gandhi-ani_625x300_25_June_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fmessage-to-opposition-if-you-want-to-be-heard-be-ready-to-listen-too-6046997%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20responsibility%20to%20listen%20and%20enable%20the%20optimal%20functioning%20of%20Parliament%20is%20intrinsic%20to%20the%20Opposition's%20right%20to%20be%20heard%20and%20assertive.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fmessage-to-opposition-if-you-want-t