C%20awarded%20posthumously%20to%20Captain%20Singh%20for%20his%20bravery%20during%20a%20fire%20incident%20in%20Siachen.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20would%20tell%20me%2C%20'I%20would%20die%20with%20the%20brass%20on%20my%20chest.%20I%20would%20not%20die%20an%20ordinary%20death%2C'%26quot%3B%20Smriti%20Singh%20recalled.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20met%20on%20the%20first%20day%20of%20college.%20I%20don't%20want%20to%20be%20dramatic%20but%20it%20was%20love%20at%20first%20sight.%20After%20a%20month%2C%20he%20got%20selected%20into%20the%20Armed%20Forces%20Medical%20College%20(AFMC).%20We%20met%20at%20an%20engineering%20college%20but%20then%20he%20got%20selected%20in%20a%20medical%20college.%20Super%20intelligent%20guy.%20From%20then%20on%2C%20after%20just%20one%20month%20of%20meeting%2C%20it%20was%20a%20long-distance%20relationship%20for%20eight%20long%20years%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%20%26quot%3BThen%20we%20decided%20to%20get%20married.%20Unfortunately%2C%20within%20two%20months%20of%20our%20marriage%2C%20he%20got%20posted%20in%20Siachen.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3ECpt%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FAnshumanSingh%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23AnshumanSingh%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20awarded%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FKirtiChakra%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23KirtiChakra%3C%2Fa%3E%20(posthumous).%20It%20was%20an%20emotional%20moment%20for%20his%20wife%20%26amp%3B%20Veer%20Nari%20Smt%20Smriti%20who%20accepted%20the%20award%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FPresident%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23President%3C%2Fa%3E%20Smt%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FDroupadiMurmu%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23DroupadiMurmu%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Smt%20Smriti%20shares%20the%20story%20of%20her%20husband's%20commitment%20%26amp%3B%20dedication%20towards%20the%20nation.%20Listen%20in!%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FSNZTwSDZ1Z%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FSNZTwSDZ1Z%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20A.%20Bharat%20Bhushan%20Babu%20(%40SpokespersonMoD)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSpokespersonMoD%2Fstatus%2F1809469003703939373%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJuly%206%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECaptain%20Singh%20was%20posted%20with%2026%20Punjab%20as%20a%20medical%20officer%20in%20the%20Siachen%20Glacier%20area.%20On%20July%2019%2C%202023%2C%20a%20short%20circuit%20led%20to%20a%20fire%20in%20an%20Indian%20Army%20ammunition%20dump%20around%203%20am.%20Captain%20Singh%20saw%20a%20fibreglass%20hut%20engulfed%20in%20flames%20and%20immediately%20acted%20to%20save%20those%20trapped%20inside.%20He%20successfully%20rescued%20four%20to%20five%20individuals%2C%20however%2C%20the%20fire%20soon%20spread%20to%20a%20nearby%20medical%20investigation%20room.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECaptain%20Singh%20went%20back%20into%20the%20blazing%20structure.%20Despite%20his%20efforts%2C%20he%20could%20not%20escape%20the%20inferno%2C%20and%20was%20trapped%20inside%20before%20dying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUnfortunately%2C%20within%20two%20months%20of%20our%20marriage%2C%20he%20got%20posted%20in%20Siachen%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Singh%20recounted.%20%26quot%3BOn%20July%2018%2C%20we%20had%20a%20long%20conversation%20about%20how%20our%20life%20would%20be%20in%20the%20next%2050%20years.%20On%20July%2019%20morning%2C%20I%20got%20a%20call%20that%20he%20is%20no%20more%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BFor%20the%20next%207-8%20hours%20we%20were%20not%20ready%20to%20accept%20that%20anything%20of%20such%20sort%20has%20happened.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNow%20that%20I%20have%20the%20Kirti%20Chakra%20in%20my%20hand%2C%20maybe%20it%20is%20true.%20But%20it's%20okay%2C%20he's%20a%20hero.%20We%20can%20manage%20a%20l