.%20During%20such%20a%20chat%20with%20Neeraj%2C%20PM%20asked%20the%20javelin%20thrower%20to%20bring%20homemade%20'churma'%20for%20him%20prepared%20by%20his%20mother.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENeeraj%20casually%20greeted%20the%20PM%2C%20saying%2C%20%26quot%3BNamaskar%20sir%2C%20kaise%20hain%3F%26quot%3B%20(Hello%20sir%2C%20how%20are%20you%3F)%20To%20which%20PM%20Modi%20replied%20with%20a%20chuckle%2C%20%26quot%3BMai%20vaisa%20hi%20hu%26quot%3B%20(I%20am%20just%20the%20same).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi%20then%20joked%2C%20%26quot%3BMera%20choorma%20abhi%20tak%20aaya%20nahi%26quot%3B%20(I%20haven't%20received%20my%20churma%20yet)%2C%20sparking%20laughter%20all%20around.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20a%20shy%20smile%2C%20Neeraj%20replied%2C%20%26quot%3BIs%20baar%20Haryana%20wala%20choorma%20khilayenge%20sir%2C%20pichli%20baar%20Delhi%20ka%20cheeni%20wala%20khaya%20tha%26quot%3B%20(This%20time%20I%20will%20treat%20you%20with%20churma%20from%20Haryana%3B%20last%20time%20we%20had%20the%20sugary%20one%20from%20Delhi).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20PM%20eagerly%20expressed%20his%20craving%20for%20homemade%20churma%2C%20saying%2C%20%26quot%3BMujhe%20tumhari%20maa%20ke%20haath%20ka%20choorma%20khana%20hai%26quot%3B%20(I%20want%20to%20savour%20churma%20made%20by%20your%20mother).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20their%20humorous%20banter%2C%20PM%20Modi%20wished%20Neeraj%20all%20the%20best%20for%20the%20Paris%20Olympics%2C%20urging%20him%20to%20stay%20fit%20and%20injury-free.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENeeraj's%20father%20Satish%20Kumar%20said%20his%20son%20detailed%20his%20training%20and%20preparations%20for%20the%20Olympics%20to%20PM%20Modi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNeeraj%20told%20PM%20that%20his%20training%20is%20going%20well%20and%20he'll%20give%20his%20all%20to%20clinch%20the%20second%20gold%20medal%20for%20the%20country%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20has%20missed%20some%20of%20the%20events%20in%20the%20past%20due%20to%20groin%20injury%20but%20now%20he%20has%2