ifically%20asked%20the%20officials%20to%20''prioritise%20rarest%20of%20rare%20cases%20and%20applications%20from%20those%20who%20are%20not%20covered%20under%20any%20existing%20scheme''.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20chief%20minister%20said%20after%20interacting%20with%20the%20flood-hit%20people%2C%20he%20had%20sent%20messages%20to%20officials%20to%20address%20their%20problems.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20us%2C%20proactive%20governance%20is%20the%20key%20to%20effective%20public%20service%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20supply%20of%20clean%20drinking%20water%2C%20he%20said%20while%20the%20flood%20has%20caused%20considerable%20damage%20across%20the%20state%2C%20the%20'Jal%20Jeevan%20Mission'%20scheme%20has%20come%20out%20as%20a%20''silver%20lining%20in%20these%20tough%20times''.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E''The%20transformative%20water%20supply%20project%20is%20supplying%20clean%20drinking%20water%20in%20these%20tough%20times''%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECachar%2C%20Kamrup%2C%20Hailakandi%2C%20Hojai%2C%20Dhubri%2C%20Nagaon%2C%20Morigaon%2C%20Goalpara%2C%20Barpeta%2C%20Dibrugarh%2C%20Nalbari%2C%20Dhemaji%2C%20Bongaigaon%2C%20Lakhimpur%2C%20Jorhat%2C%20Sonitpur%2C%20Kokrajhar%2C%20Karimganj%2C%20South%20Salmara%2C%20Darrang%20and%20Tinsukia%20are%20among%20the%20districts%20affected%20by%20the%20flood.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20toll%20in%20this%20year's%20flood%2C%20landslides%20and%20storms%20was%2064%2C%20according%20to%20the%20bulletin%20of%20the%20Assam%20State%20Disaster%20Management%20Authority%20(ASDMA).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDhubri%20with%20a%20population%20of%207%2C75%2C721%2C%20Darrang%20with%201%2C86%2C108%2C%20Cachar%20with%201%2C75%2C231%2C%20Barpeta%20with%201%2C39%2C399%20and%20Morigaon%20with%201%2C46%2C045%20are%20among%20the%20worst-hit%20districts%2C%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAltogether%2047%2C103%20affected%20people%20have%20taken%20shelter%20in%20612%20camps%2C%20while%204%2C18%2C614%20inmates%20in%20non-relief%20camps%20have%20been%20provided%20with%20relief%20materials.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFlood%20in%20urban%20areas%20of%20three%20districts%20of%20Kamrup%20(Metropolitan)%2C%20Kamrup%20and%20Dibrugarh%20was%20also%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECabinet%20ministers%20are%20also%20camping%20in%20various%20flood-affected%20districts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Sarma%20said%20he%20and%20his%20entire%20team%20are%20on%20the%20ground%20to%20''assess%20the%20damage%20caused%20by%20the%20floods%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20working%20tirelessly%20to%20hear%20people's%20grievances%20and%20solve%20their%20issues%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20chief%20minister%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Brahmaputra%20river%20is%20flowing%20above%20the%20danger%20mark%20at%20Nimatighat%2C%20Guwahati%2C%20Goalpara%20and%20Dhubri.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIts%20tributaries%20Burhi%20Dihing%20at%20Chenimari%2C%20Dikhou%20at%20Sivasagar%2C%20Disang%20at%20Nanglamuraghat%2C%20Dhansiri%20at%20Numaligarh%2C%20Jia%20Bharali%20at%20NT%20Road%20crossing%2C%20and%20Kopili%20at%20Kampur%20and%20Dharamtul%20are%20also%20flowing%20above%20the%20danger%20levels.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Barak%20river%20is%20flowing%20above%20the%20danger%20mark%20at%20AP%20Ghat%2C%20BP%20Ghat%2C%20Chota%20Bakra%20and%20Fuletral%2C%20and%20its%20tributaries%20Dhaleswari%20at%20Gharmura%2C%20Katakhal%20at%20Matizuri%20and%20Kushiyara%20at%20Karimganj%20town.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInfrastructure%20damaged%20by%20the%20floods%20includes%20225%20roads%20and%2010%20bridges%20among%20others%2C%20the%20bulletin%20added.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1720255860000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2F0156978_assam-flood-ani_625x300_02_July_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-