n%20is%20removed%20from%20the%20office%2C%20and%20the%20new%20principal%2C%20Sherlyn%20Massey%2C%20is%20seated%20amid%20applause%20and%20clapping%20from%20the%20staff.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ECase%20Registered%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Bishop%20Dan%2C%20Shirley%20Massey%20was%20appointed%20as%20the%20new%20principal%20following%20Ms%20Solomon's%20termination.%20However%2C%20upon%20Ms%20Massey's%20arrival%2C%20Ms%20Solomon%20allegedly%20locked%20herself%20in%20the%20principal's%20office.%20When%20the%20door%20was%20forcibly%20opened%2C%20some%20teachers%20removed%20Ms%20Solomon%20from%20her%20chair.%20Bishop%20Dan%20has%20claimed%20that%20Ms%20Solomon%20has%20registered%20a%20case%20against%20the%20group%20for%20sexual%20abuse.%20However%2C%20he%20contends%20that%20despite%20Ms%20Solomon's%20claims%2C%20video%20and%20CCTV%20footage%20show%20no%20physical%20contact.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBishop%20Dan%20has%20provided%20additional%20videos%20to%20authorities.%20Nevertheless%2C%20videos%20of%20the%20alleged%20mistreatment%20of%20Principal%20Parul%20Solomon%20have%20not%20yet%20been%20released%20publicly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20Ms%20Solomon's%20complaint%2C%20a%20case%20has%20been%20registered%20against%20several%20individuals%2C%20including%20NL%20Dan%2C%20Bishop%20Maurice%20Edgar%20Dan%2C%20Vinita%20Isubius%2C%20Sanjeet%20Lal%2C%20Vishal%20Navel%20Singh%2C%20RK%20Singh%2C%20Arun%20Mojs%2C%20Tarun%20Vyas%2C%20Abhishek%20Vyas%2C%20and%20others.%20Meanwhile%2C%20the%20accused%20have%20submitted%20videos%20to%20the%20police%2C%20who%20are%20currently%20investigating%20the%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBishop%20Dan%20has%20accused%20Ms%20Solomon%20of%20embezzling%20Rs%202.40%20crore%20from%20the%20school%20during%20her%20tenure%20as%20principal.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1720252620000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2Fntoi053o_up-principal-_625x300_06_July_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https