0their%20eyes%2C%E2%80%9D%20IAS%20Vivek%20Johnson%20tells%3Cstrong%3E%20The%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20a%20demo%20house%20which%20can%20be%20replicated%20in%20the%20housing%20scheme%20under%20the%20Pradhan%20Mantri%20Awas%20Yojana.%20By%20constructing%20such%20homes%2C%20tonnes%20of%20plastic%20waste%20from%20villages%20and%20cities%20can%20be%20utilised.%20In%20future%2C%20if%20you%20ever%20desire%20to%20dismantle%20the%20house%2C%20you%20can%20reuse%20and%20recycle%20all%20the%20demolished%20plastic%20material%2C%20which%20is%20not%20possible%20in%20reinforced%20concrete%20structures.%20By%20adopting%20such%20a%20house%2C%20you%20protect%20the%20environment%2C%20use%20less%20natural%20resources%2C%20reduce%20plastic%20waste%2C%20and%20generate%20employment%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Dr%20Balmukund.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIncluding%20collection%2C%20machinery%2C%20and%20labour%2C%20the%20cost%20of%20constructing%20the%20plastic%20house%20was%20Rs%209%20lakh%2C%20claims%20the%20doctor.%20Of%20the%20total%20cost%2C%20the%20Zila%20Parishad%20sanctioned%20Rs%205%20lakh%20(the%20upper%20limit%20for%20the%20construction%20of%20the%20demo%20house).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20comparatively%2020%20percent%20less%20than%20the%20conventional%20cemented%20house.%20I%20invested%20the%20remaining%20amount%20so%20that%20funds%20do%20not%20become%20an%20issue%20and%20we%20have%20an%20example%20for%20others%20to%20adopt.%20As%20citizens%2C%20we%20need%20to%20understand%20our%20responsibilities%20towards%20protecting%20the%20environment.%20I%20am%20doing%20my%20bit%2C%20and%20I%20seek%20public%20and%20Government%20support%20to%20promote%20such%20houses%20to%20benefit%20all%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20concludes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3B%20All%20photos%3A%20Dr%20Balmukund%20Paliwal.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1720102772000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploa