24%2F07%2Fmeru-daycare-1720005938-500x333.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fmeru-daycare-1720005938-768x511.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fmeru-daycare-1720005938-150x100.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-355394%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221006%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EMeru%20International%20School%20has%20launched%20a%20daycare%20centre%20called%20Meru%20Aveksha.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20he%20shared%20this%20with%20Ramu%20Rao%20Jupally%2C%20the%20vice%20chairman%20of%20My%20Home%20Constructions%2C%20Ramu%20Rao%20immediately%20agreed%20to%20help%2C%20and%20the%20team%20reached%20out%20to%20Meghana%20Gorukanti%C2%A0%20Jupally%2C%20who%20runs%20Meru%20International%20School%2C%20to%20find%20a%20solution.%20How%20could%20they%20provide%20early%20childhood%20education%20in%20a%20nurturing%20and%20safe%20environment%3F%20By%20building%20a%20daycare%20centre-cum-play%20school%20called%20the%20Meru%20Aveksha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20Meru%20Aveksha%20centre%20was%20opened%20last%20year%20at%20an%20upcoming%20residential%20project%20by%20the%20My%20Home%20Group%20in%20Kokapet%2C%20Hyderabad.%20Over%20the%20past%2012%20months%2C%20two%20more%20centres%20were%20opened%20in%20the%20city.%20The%20three%20centres%20cater%20to%20over%20150%20children%2C%20from%20infants%20to%2012-year-olds%2C%20providing%20them%20a%20safe%20place%20to%20stay%20during%20the%20day%2C%20while%20empowering%20them%20with%20the%20necessary%20skill%20sets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ESafety%2C%20education%20and%20food%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Meru%20Aveksha%20team%20first%20spoke%20to%20the%20parents%20and%20children%20of%20the%20migrant%20labourers%20to%20understand%20the%20major%20gaps.%20They%20found%20that%20there%20was%20no%20facility%20for%20these%20children%20to%20spend%20ti