0Pachauri%20had%20been%20preparing%20for%20the%20government%20examinations%20for%20nearly%20four%20years%20but%20was%20unable%20to%20achieve%20success.%20Roughly%20two%20years%20back%2C%20he%20was%20standing%20at%20the%20crossroads.%20He%20had%20two%20choices%20%E2%80%94%20continue%20to%20strive%20for%20government%20exams%20or%20become%20a%20farmer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20eventually%20chose%20the%20latter%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20the%2030-year-old.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20after%20completing%20his%20higher%20education%20in%20mechanical%20engineering%20in%202017%20that%20Gaurav%20%E2%80%94%20like%20his%20friends%20%E2%80%94%20started%20preparing%20for%20the%20Rajasthan%20Administrative%20Services.%20%E2%80%9CI%20went%20to%20Delhi%20to%20prepare%20for%20the%20exams.%20I%20tried%20my%20best%20but%20I%20did%20not%20get%20good%20results.%20So%20I%20started%20believing%20that%20government%20exams%20were%20not%20for%20me%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20bid%20to%20do%20something%20unique%2C%20Gaurav%20ventured%20into%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F334671%2Fmaharashtra-farmers-oyster-pearl-cultivation-battle-drought-suicide-earn-income%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efreshwater%20pearl%20farming%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%E2%80%9CI%20would%20keep%20watching%20television%20programmes%20where%20I%20was%20introduced%20to%20new%20types%20of%20farming%20like%20freshwater%20pearl%20farming.%20I%20found%20it%20interesting%20as%20one%20could%20earn%20handsomely%20by%20selling%20pearls.%20But%20it%20was%20risky%20as%20well%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMore%20than%20the%20risk%20of%20taking%20up%20pearl%20farming%2C%20Gaurav%20feared%20breaking%20the%20idea%20to%20his%20family.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20shared%20the%20idea%20with%20my%20parents%2C%20they%20were%20not%20convinced%20at%20all.%20My%20family%20had%20been%20growing%20traditional%20crops%20like%20wheat%2C%20millet