-heading%5C%22%3EEarned%202.5x%20of%20investment%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20mid-2022%2C%20Gaurav%20eventually%20convinced%20his%20family%20and%20went%20to%20see%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F267186%2Fpearl-farming-cultivation-oyster-shell-home-made-pond-set-up-ashok-manwani-kuljana%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epearl%20farming%20%3C%2Fa%3Eponds%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20and%20West%20Bengal.%20He%20also%20attended%20a%20five-day%20training%20at%20the%20Central%20Institute%20for%20Freshwater%20Aquaculture%20(CIFA)%20in%20Odisha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%2C%20I%20was%20taught%20the%20nitty%20gritty%20of%20pearl%20farming.%20I%20learnt%20how%20to%20source%20raw%20material%2C%20how%20to%20nucleate%20mussels%2C%20what%20food%20to%20offer%20the%20mussels%20and%20their%20surgical%20procedure%2C%20and%20how%20to%20make%20both%20designer%20pearls%20and%20round%20pearls.%20With%20this%20training%2C%20which%20cost%20me%20Rs%208%2C000%2C%20I%20became%20confident%20about%20implementing%20it%20on%20the%20ground.%20I%20also%20received%20the%20certification%20to%20practise%20pearl%20farming%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20September%202022%2C%20Gaurav%20prepared%20a%20pond%20of%20150%20x%2080%20feet%20in%20his%20village%20in%20Bharatpur%20district%20and%20added%201.15%20lakh%20mussels%20to%20the%20pond.%20Interestingly%2C%20he%20roped%20in%20other%20small%20farmers%20in%20the%20projects%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CInitially%2C%20I%E2%80%99d%20thought%20of%20starting%20pearl%20farming%20at%20a%20small%20scale%20but%20as%20and%20when%20I%20discussed%20this%20with%20more%20and%20more%20farmers%2C%20they%20became%20interested%20in%20investing%20in%20the%20work.%20Of%201.15%20lakh%20mussels%2C%20I%20had%20invested%20in%2050%2C000%20mussels%20personally%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGaurav%20started%20the%20project%20by%20investing%20Rs%2021%20lakh%2C%20o