0role%20model.%20%E2%80%9CNot%20many%20younger%20siblings%20get%20the%20opportunity%20to%20see%20their%20elder%20siblings%20grow%20up%20in%20front%20of%20them.%20I%20salute%20her%20willpower%20and%20I%20often%20tell%20her%20that%20she%20is%20the%20main%20character%20of%20my%20life!%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsha%20smiles%20as%20she%20remembers%20the%20day%20her%20%3Cem%3Edidi%20%3C%2Fem%3E(elder%20sister)%20got%20admission%20into%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F170564%2Fahmedabad-uttarayan-rescue-crane-doc-inspiring%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eorthopaedics%20%3C%2Fa%3Edepartment%20at%20the%20BJ%20Medical%20College%2C%20Ahmedabad.%20%E2%80%9CI%20baked%20a%20cake%20and%20we%20celebrated%20it%20like%20a%20festival!%E2%80%9D%20she%20exclaims.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdversity%20had%20taught%20the%20family%20to%20cherish%20the%20small%20wins.%20%E2%80%9CI%20remember%20the%20first%20time%20after%20the%20accident%20when%20my%20sister%20was%20able%20to%20open%20the%20cap%20on%20the%20toothpaste%20tube%20and%20brush%20her%20teeth%20by%20herself%2C%E2%80%9D%20Isha%20continues.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20memory%20that%20eclipses%20all%20others%20for%20Isha%20is%20the%20day%20Sakshi%20took%20her%20first%20steps%20without%20support.%20%E2%80%9CFor%20us%2C%20it%20was%20equivalent%20to%20a%20toddler%20taking%20their%20first%20steps.%20We%20screamed%20in%20joy%20and%20danced!%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20argues%20that%20while%20these%20might%20seem%20small%20feats%20to%20others%2C%20they%20were%20equal%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F353374%2Fsoftware-engineers-techies-left-quit-jobs-career-food-business-startup-entrepreneur-inspiring%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebig%20milestones%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20the%20family.%20And%20Sakshi%20agrees%2C%20adding%20that%20their%20support%20was%20un