y%20have%20a%20notion%20that%20it%E2%80%99s%20small%20and%20not%20viable.%20Nothing%20can%20be%20farther%20from%20the%20truth%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Smarika%20Chandrakar.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20enterprising%20MBA%20graduate%20grew%20up%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F348905%2Fhydroponics-training-workshop-in-gujarat-india-rasik-nakum-one-farm-hydroponics-rajkot-teaching-soil-less-water-less-farming%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efarming%20family%20%3C%2Fa%3Ein%20Charmudiya%20village%20in%20Chattisgarh.%20Her%20childhood%20was%20spent%20in%20the%20lush%20green%20paddy%20fields%20with%20her%20father%20and%20grandfather%20where%20she%20learnt%20her%20first%20lessons%20about%20life%20and%20farming.%20Like%20any%20other%20business%2C%20they%20had%20good%20and%20bad%20times%20as%20well%20which%20the%20young%20girl%20was%20quick%20to%20adapt%20to.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20it%20came%20to%20choosing%20a%20career%2C%20she%20chose%20to%20pursue%20an%20engineering%20degree%20in%20Computer%20Science%20in%20Raipur%2C%20followed%20by%20an%20MBA%20from%20Pune.%20After%20working%20as%20a%20senior%20business%20development%20executive%20for%20over%20five%20years%20in%20Pune%2C%20she%20decided%20to%20move%20to%20Raipur%20to%20be%20closer%20to%20her%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20allowed%20her%20to%20spend%20weekends%20at%20home%2C%20which%20were%20invariably%20at%20the%20farm.%20She%20started%20learning%20the%20finer%20nuances%20of%20paddy%20farming%20and%20their%20discussions%20at%20dinner%20turned%20into%20how%20they%20could%20improve%20productivity%20and%20the%20profits.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fsmarika1-1719549336.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Smarika%20r