cre%20in%20the%20first%20year.%20We%20sold%20it%20in%20local%20%3Cem%3Emandis%3C%2Fem%3E%20(marts)%20and%20in%20other%20cities%20like%20Visakhapatnam%2C%20Patna%2C%20Kolkata%2C%20New%20Delhi%2C%20Bengaluru%20and%20more.%20I%20have%20tied-up%20with%20brokers%20with%20whom%20I%20pre-decide%20the%20rates%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%20tomatoes%2C%20she%20also%20grows%20bottle%20gourd%2C%20cucumber%20and%20brinjal.%20The%20sowing%20and%20harvesting%20season%20is%20between%20May%20to%20March%2C%20with%20the%20cycle%20roughly%20around%20three%20months%2C%20she%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhile%20we%20would%20only%20be%20able%20to%20harvest%20paddy%20twice%20a%20year%2C%20we%20are%20able%20to%20harvest%20vegetables%20many%20more%20times.%20It%E2%80%99s%20also%20much%20more%20profitable%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20same%20%3Cem%3EEconomic%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%20article%2C%20Dilip%20Rajan%20shared%2C%20%E2%80%9CFor%20instance%2C%20a%20thousand%20square%20metres%20of%20land%20planted%20with%20bitter%20gourd%20will%20give%20a%20farmer%20roughly%20the%20same%20income%20as%20one%20hectare%20planted%20for%20rice.%20Vegetables%20can%20be%20harvested%20quickly%20(45-55%20days)%2C%20and%203-4%20crops%20can%20be%20cultivated%20throughout%20the%20year%20to%20meet%20the%20increased%20demand%20for%20vegetables%20and%20changes%20in%20food%20consumption.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFarming%20is%20a%20viable%20career%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20past%20three%20years%2C%20Smarika%20has%20been%20cultivating%20a%20variety%20of%20vegetables%20on%20her%20land.%20She%20now%20plans%20to%20add%2015%20acres%20more%20this%20year%20to%20her%20existing%2020.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201600px)%20100vw%2C%201600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fs